cast.original_title: Miraculous World : Shanghai, la légende de Ladydragon
cast.overview: On school break, Marinette heads to Shanghai to meet Adrien. But after arriving, Marinette loses all her stuff, including the Miraculous that allows her to turn into Ladybug!
cast.title: Miraculous World: Shanghai - The Legend of Ladydragon

details.biography: Geneviève Doang is a French-Asian actress of Chinese descent born in Paris, bilingual in English. She is skilled in Kung Fu and stage combat and known for her voice acting career, remembered for being the French voice of Ciri in The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt, D.Va in Overwatch, Lunafreya in Final Fantasy XV and Evangelyne in Wakfu.
details.name: Geneviève Doang
